episodes.title: Trauma Twins | E2 Growing Up in a Church Cult
episodes.description: Growing up in the evangelical mid-west has led to many "interesting" experiences and even more challenging philosophical views. After Dave was forced to attend an ex-gay conversion ministry, Sarah began questioning the role the church and God played in her life. And yet, these experiences spurred the exploration necessary for them to find the paths that truly aligned with who we knew ourselves to be.
